text: Igor Mikhailovich Kalashnikov (; born 22 January 1993) is a Russian sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Russian male canoeists Category:Canoeists at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics
